name: BNTOBER
description: Welcome to the Bntober Month! Meme was inspired by a CZ post mentioning October as BNTOBER month showing bullish vibes for the BNB chain and it's ecosystem and expecting it to go higher this month. Project is launched through Fourmeme platform on BNB chain, upon launch it went to straight $1.6M but then dropped down to under $100K market cap. Right now some community members are CTOing it and making sure it is a huge success.
